FBIS3-42307 "jptot007__l94093" JPRS-TOT-94-007-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 16 February 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA YEMEN Foreign Minister Says `Afghan Arabs' in Country NC0902065194 Cairo MENA in Arabic 2225 GMT 8 Feb 94 NC0902065194 Cairo MENA Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Cairo, 8 Feb (MENA)-- [passage omitted] In statements to AL-AHRAM published Wednesday, Yemeni Foreign Minister Muhammad Salim Basindwah noted that charges that his country is providing refuge for terrorists might be prompted by some Afghan Arabs' infiltration of Yemen. He said that their infiltration takes place secretly and without the security authorities' consent. [passage omitted]
